1
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:22,060
乐高DC超级英雄：闪电侠

2
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:44,390
漂亮
Booyah!

3
00:00:44,390 --> 00:00:46,290
半人 半机器
Half man, half machine.

4
00:00:46,860 --> 00:00:48,660
整个都厉害
All awesome.

5
00:00:48,660 --> 00:00:50,490
我简直就是忍者遇上游侠
I'm like a ninja meets an acrobat.

6
00:00:50,490 --> 00:00:51,730
我是忍者蝙啊
I'm a ninjabat!

7
00:00:51,730 --> 00:00:53,290
说不定我也是蝙蝠家族中的一员呢
Maybe I'm in the bat family.

8
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:55,060
梦想果然还是要有的
Dreams do come true.

9
00:00:55,060 --> 00:00:56,300
我实在是……
I am so...

10
00:01:01,100 --> 00:01:02,410
太牛逼了
Amazing.

11
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,680
啊？
Huh?

12
00:01:21,590 --> 00:01:23,290
怎么也不让我牛逼一回 是不？
Couldn't let me have it,could you?

13
00:01:23,290 --> 00:01:26,560
你在正义大厅[著名的正义联盟行动基地]参观的最后一站就是这里
And your tour of the Hall of Justice concludes here.

14
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,990
我们特别设计的
In our specially designed

15
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,270
全国最顶级的高精尖训练设施
state-of-the-art training facility.

16
00:01:30,270 --> 00:01:32,070
原子侠 这位是钢骨
Atom, meet Cyborg.

17
00:01:32,070 --> 00:01:33,740
机械专家钢骨
Cyber mechanical specialist

18
00:01:33,740 --> 00:01:36,600
还有我们正义联盟的阳光小射线
and the League's little ray of sunshine.

19
00:01:36,610 --> 00:01:38,410
嗨 原子侠
Hey, Atom.

20
00:01:38,410 --> 00:01:40,840
啊 家犬亚种
Ah, Canis lupus familiaris.

21
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:44,440
一个常见的说法认为 狗是人类最好的朋友
It's a common hypothesis that dog is man's best friend.

22
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:48,090
但是，呃……不是我说的
But, uh... Not mine.

23
00:01:49,090 --> 00:01:51,490
哇哦，酷！哦……
Whoa, cool! Oh...

24
00:01:51,490 --> 00:01:55,060
“原子侠”我明白你的名字是怎么来的了
"The Atom."I see what you did there

25
00:01:55,060 --> 00:01:57,990
你可以缩小成任何小玩意啊
with your name and you shrinking down all tiny and stuff.

26
00:01:57,990 --> 00:01:59,360
别紧张 原子侠
Relax, Atom.

27
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:01,330
这是大A，蝙蝠犬
This is Ace, the Bat-Hound.

28
00:02:01,330 --> 00:02:03,930
他只是评估你一下
He's just evaluating you.

29
00:02:03,930 --> 00:02:06,700
根据我的科学评估
Well, in my scientific evaluation,

30
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:08,970
大A可以说是非常吓人了
Ace is very intimidating.

31
00:02:08,970 --> 00:02:09,940
可不是嘛
Tell me about it.

32
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:14,280
跟动物打交道的第一课
Lesson one with animals.

33
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:16,580
永远别胆怯
Never show weakness.

34
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:19,510
伙计 我觉得我得换机油了
Man, I think I need an oil change.

35
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:22,250
蝙蝠侠，我真不知道你还有一个……
Batman, I didn't know you had a...

36
00:02:22,250 --> 00:02:23,820
呃 超级宠物
Uh... Super-Pet.

37
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:26,790
大A可不只是一只宠物
Ace the Bat-Hound is more than a pet.

38
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:27,950
他是最好的小伙伴
He's the best sidekick

39
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:30,190
一个穿披风的骑士梦寐以求那种
a caped crusader could ever have.

40
00:02:30,190 --> 00:02:32,160
那罗宾呢？
What about Robin?

41
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:35,630
你是不是最强伙伴呀？没错你就是
Aren't you the best sidekick? Yes, you are, yes you are.

42
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:38,200
我也好想要蝙蝠侠给我揉揉肚子
Aw, I want a Bat belly rub.

43
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,770
所以 原子侠
So, Atom.

44
00:02:39,770 --> 00:02:42,600
现在正义大厅你也参观过了……
Now that you've seen the Hall of Justice...

45
00:02:42,610 --> 00:02:44,340
你有什么想法？
What do you think?

46
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:46,670
想不想加入正义联盟？
Would you like to become a member of the Justice League?

47
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:49,140
我……
I...

48
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:50,540
等一会儿再回答
Hold your diminutive answer.

49
00:02:50,550 --> 00:02:51,880
跟我来
Follow me.

50
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:55,550
快点啦 塑胶人 这是麻烦事警报
Come on, Plas,it's the trouble alert.

51
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:57,920
但是我好饿啊，得有人送我一程
But I'm starving.I need a pick-me-up.

52
00:02:57,920 --> 00:03:00,050
拿这个送你一程怎么样？
How's this for a pick-me-up?

53
00:03:00,060 --> 00:03:03,990
一份快餐外卖就能送你好大一程
One order of fast food to give you a boost.

54
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:06,090
啊？什么？喂！
Huh? What? Hey!

55
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:10,200
想当团队加油员你还差得远呢 火风暴
Way to be a team motivator, Firestorm.

56
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:17,240
看看今天是谁需要我们帮助
Let's see who needs our help today.

57
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,640
我是路易丝·莱恩 为大家带来爆炸性消息
This is Lois Lane with Breaking News.

58
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:21,280
哥谭市的犯罪王子
Gotham City's clown prince of crime,

59
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:23,980
小丑 已经侵入了我们挚爱的城市
the Joker, has invaded our beloved city.

60
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:26,780
啊
Ah.

61
00:03:26,780 --> 00:03:28,620
阳光大都会啊
Sunny Metropolis.

62
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:32,250
摆脱哥谭黑暗骑士的完美度假胜地
The perfect getaway from Gotham's Dark Knight.

63
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:34,320
想来一次小小的度假
Nothing like a little vacation

64
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:37,020
没什么比把我的小宠物放在脚底下遛遛更好的了
to put the pep back in my step.

65
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:54,610
哦我的天呐
Oh, my!

66
00:03:54,610 --> 00:03:56,810
小丑在城市里大放毒气
The Joker's gassing the city.

67
00:03:56,810 --> 00:04:00,720
谁能来阻止这个搞破坏的小丑呢？
Who can stop this ruinous jester?

68
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:04,220
帮帮我们吧！正义联盟 超人！
Help us!Justice League, Superman.

69
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:05,420
救救我们！
Save us!

70
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:11,130
天啊！路易丝遇上麻烦了
Great Scott!Lois is in trouble.

71
00:04:11,130 --> 00:04:12,230
又一次
Again.

72
00:04:12,230 --> 00:04:15,530
好啦队员们 我们出发吧
All right, team,gear up and let's go.

73
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:17,000
原子侠 这是你的大好机会
Atom, this is your chance

74
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,900
加入正义联盟一展身手
to join he Justice League in action.

75
00:04:18,900 --> 00:04:20,970
- 你准备好了吗？ - 我 呃……
-Are you ready? - I, uh...

76
00:04:20,970 --> 00:04:22,100
不要有压力
No pressure.

77
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:23,570
我们明白你是超级英雄里的新人
We know you're new at being a superhero.

78
00:04:23,570 --> 00:04:24,870
如果你愿意的话 你可以留在这里
If you want, you can stay here

79
00:04:24,870 --> 00:04:26,310
跟大A和克利皮托一起玩一会儿
and hang out with Ace and Krypto.

80
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:27,580
克利皮托？
Krypto?

81
00:04:29,210 --> 00:04:31,050
还有一只超级宠物？
Another Super-Pet?

82
00:04:31,050 --> 00:04:33,750
算了 我宁可选小丑也不要狗
Yeah, I'll take the clown over the canine.

83
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:36,050
越快越好
The sooner, the better.

84
00:04:42,990 --> 00:04:46,290
哦 星球日报的新闻大楼
Ooh, the Daily Planet news building.

85
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:48,700
唔 导游管这个叫
Hmm, the visitors' guide calls it

86
00:04:48,700 --> 00:04:51,770
“大都会市天际线的明珠”
"The jewel of the Metropolis skyline."

87
00:04:52,540 --> 00:04:54,670
真没劲
Meh. Kinda boring.

88
00:04:54,670 --> 00:04:56,670
咱们来翻修一下吧！
Let's renovate!

89
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,610
那小丑真不要脸
The nerve of that clown.

90
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:07,510
他居然在践踏我们大都会市天际线的明珠
He's tromping all over the jewel of the Metropolis skyline.

91
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:09,180
他还乱穿马路不守交规
And he's jaywalking.

92
00:05:09,180 --> 00:05:10,880
让我们把他拿下
Let's take him down.

93
00:05:14,690 --> 00:05:16,960
还有欢迎委员会啊？
The welcoming committee.For me?

94
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:18,890
幸好我带了奶油小点心
Good thing I brought pastry.

95
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,630
哇哦 那是椰子奶油吗？
Ooh, is that coconut cream?

96
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:27,070
是柠檬蛋白酥
Lemon meringue.

97
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:28,340
带自爆那种
With a bang.

98
00:05:29,970 --> 00:05:33,310
撑住啊 要撞啦！
Brace for impact!

99
00:05:36,250 --> 00:05:39,850
多么美丽又安全的公园一日游啊
What a beautiful, perfectly safe day at the park.

100
00:05:47,590 --> 00:05:50,020
早知道我就开自己的隐形飞机了
- I should've taken my jet.- Ooh. Ooh.

101
00:05:50,030 --> 00:05:53,660
我还能挺住
I'm holding it together.

102
00:05:54,860 --> 00:05:56,630
好丢人啊
Oh, this is embarrassing.

103
00:05:59,100 --> 00:06:02,100
也没那么好笑吧 考虑下别人的感受好不好
It's not that funny.A little consideration here.

104
00:06:02,110 --> 00:06:03,140
路易丝 钢骨
Lois, Cyborg.

105
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:06,270
你俩冷静点！
Try to stay calm!

106
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:09,680
我还能听见！
I can still hear you.

107
00:06:13,450 --> 00:06:15,150
现在这情况属于正常操作吗？
Is this normally how it goes?

108
00:06:15,150 --> 00:06:17,920
正常啊 但是一般来说不会笑成这样
Yeah, but usually with a little less laughter.

109
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,620
这个笑法很危险
That laughter is dangerous.

110
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:20,920
我们得帮帮这些人
We've gotta help these people

111
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,520
趁他们还没把自己笑死
before they laugh themselves to death.

112
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:25,630
而且要在小丑祸害其它人之前阻止他
And stop the Joker before he endangers anyone else.

113
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:27,130
那我们就分头行动吧
Then let's divide and conquer.

114
00:06:27,130 --> 00:06:30,030
对 我们得用闪电般的速度把这堆乱摊子清理干净
Yup, we'll have this mess cleaned up in a flash.

115
00:06:30,030 --> 00:06:32,170
说到这个 闪电侠哪儿去了？
Speaking of,where is the Flash?

116
00:06:32,170 --> 00:06:34,500
我好几分钟以前就把警报发出去了
I sent out the Justice alert minutes ago.

117
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,900
一级警报
Priority one.

118
00:06:35,910 --> 00:06:39,240
巴里很清楚我对迟到的看法
Barry knows how I feel about tardiness.

119
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:48,650
快点 巴里 起床啦
Come on, Barry. Get up.

120
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:52,420
一下……
And one...

121
00:06:52,420 --> 00:06:54,720
……两千
And 2,000.

122
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,890
好了 我起来了
Okay, I'm up.

123
00:06:55,890 --> 00:06:57,460
冲个澡
Shower time.

124
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,870
下次真的得记住要等水热了再进去洗
Whoa, I have got to remember to wait for the water to warm up before jumping in.

125
00:07:04,530 --> 00:07:06,970
不错
Nice.

126
00:07:06,970 --> 00:07:10,340
好啦中城 让我们开始派对吧
All right, Central City,let's get this party started.

127
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:14,010
嘿！你撞了我的车！
Hey, hey, hey, you hit my car!

128
00:07:14,010 --> 00:07:16,610
- 搞成这样谁来收拾啊？ - 我？明明是你撞我
- Who's gonna take care of this?- Me? You hit me.

129
00:07:16,610 --> 00:07:19,420
我非告得你倾家荡产不可
I'm gonna sue you for every brick you've got.

130
00:07:21,050 --> 00:07:22,420
谢谢 闪电侠！
Thanks, Flash!

131
00:07:22,420 --> 00:07:23,950
那就是闪电侠
That guy's Flash.

132
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:26,390
你们好啊 小鸟
Hidey ho, birdies.

133
00:07:26,390 --> 00:07:28,960
哦 小心看路啊 早上好啊 童子军52号编队
Ooh, watch your step.Good morning, Troop 52.

134
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,730
哈喽 热狗
Hello, hot dog.

135
00:07:30,730 --> 00:07:33,890
不用上学了  不用上学了
- No school.- No way. No school?

136
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:35,960
喔！多谢了 闪电侠！
Whoa! Thanks, Flash!

137
00:07:35,970 --> 00:07:37,870
谢谢 闪电侠
Thanks, Flash.

138
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:41,440
谢谢闪电侠！谢谢闪电侠！
- Thanks, Flash!- Thanks, Flash!

139
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:46,910
哇！
Whoa!

140
00:07:46,910 --> 00:07:48,840
谢啦 闪电侠！
Thanks, Flash!

141
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:50,110
才起床五分钟
Five minutes out of bed

142
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:51,680
就做了这么多事
and look at all the good I've done.

143
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,310
轮到大都会了
Time to get to Metropolis

144
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,450
来见识一下正义……
to meet up with the Justice...

145
00:07:54,450 --> 00:07:55,550
哦 这个咕噜咕噜的声音我懂
Oh, I know that grumble.

146
00:07:55,550 --> 00:07:57,720
它是在说 甜甜圈 现在！
And it's saying,"Donuts, now!"

147
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:59,750
最好吃的甜甜圈在哪里？
And where are the best donuts?

148
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:01,060
哥谭市
Gotham City.

149
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:08,500
所有中了毒气的人都已经安全撤离了
All the victims are safely evacuated.

150
00:08:10,630 --> 00:08:11,870
塑胶人
Plastic Man,

151
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:13,600
你也中了小丑的毒气了吗？
were you infected by Joker's gas?

152
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:16,810
没有 都是因为他们笑的那样儿 太搞笑了
No, it's all this laughing.It's hilarious.

153
00:08:19,340 --> 00:08:20,710
救我！
Help me!

154
00:08:23,010 --> 00:08:24,380
塑胶 严肃点
Plas, get serious,

155
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:26,550
我们必须找到治好这些市民的方法
we have to find a cure for these civilians.

156
00:08:26,550 --> 00:08:30,020
我觉得如果我能改变小丑毒气的分子结构
I wonder if I can alter the molecular structure of Joker's gas

157
00:08:30,020 --> 00:08:31,120
就能造出解毒剂
to create a cure.

158
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,760
- 怎么做？ - 在这等着
- How?- Wait here.

159
00:08:33,890 --> 00:08:35,190
好的
Okay.

160
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:41,360
假设
Hypothesis.

161
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,430
以这个大小我应该就能找到小丑毒气中
At this size I should be able to find trace elements

162
00:08:43,430 --> 00:08:46,630
飘浮在这个地区空气中的微量元素
of Joker's gas still wafting around the area.

163
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:48,140
啊哈！
Aha!

164
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:50,200
一个小丑毒气分子
A Joker gas molecule.

165
00:08:50,210 --> 00:08:52,270
找到这个没啥好玩的
There's nothing funny about this.

166
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:54,480
现在来做个小小的实验
Now for a little experiment.

167
00:08:57,510 --> 00:09:00,110
他在那儿呢 让我来揍扁这个小丑
- There he is.- I've got this clown.

168
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,750
永远不要低估小丑的实力 火风暴
Never underestimate the Joker, Firestorm.

169
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:05,190
我绕到他背后去 然后我们用……
I'll fly around behind him and then we'll take him by...

170
00:09:05,190 --> 00:09:06,520
啊？
Huh?

171
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,560
惊不惊喜？
Surprise?

172
00:09:11,990 --> 00:09:13,630
这下惨了 老兄
Not cool, man.

173
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:17,360
蝙蝠侠会让我把这个糗事记一辈子的
Batman will never let me live this down.

174
00:09:17,370 --> 00:09:21,670
是谁总是逗我乐啊
Whoo hoos always bring a smile to my face.

175
00:09:23,610 --> 00:09:25,910
你得比那个快才能
You've got to be faster than that

176
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:28,180
偷偷潜入小丑身边
to sneak up on the Joker.

177
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:32,880
闪电侠去哪儿了？
Where is Flash?

178
00:09:38,190 --> 00:09:39,920
那是闪电侠！
It's the Flash!

179
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:42,230
天底下最好吃的甜甜圈
Best donut ever.

180
00:09:44,230 --> 00:09:45,790
甜甜圈安全！
Saved the donut.

181
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:48,500
那谁来救你啊
But who's gonna save you?

182
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:49,900
冰冻队长？
Captain Cold?

183
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:52,900
我今天唯一感兴趣的霜就是这块甜甜圈上的糖霜
The only frosting I'm interested in today is on this donut.

184
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:54,100
马上投降的话 我们就把今天这事当成是
Give up now and we'll chalk it up

185
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:56,340
全球变暖的祸
to hysteria over global warming.

186
00:09:57,570 --> 00:10:01,040
才不是 今天是全球冷冻的祸
Instead, let's chalk it up to global freezing.

187
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:05,310
全球冷冻？那根本都不是个正经词儿好吧
"Global freezing"?That doesn't even make sense.

188
00:10:05,310 --> 00:10:08,110
拜托 你可比这个要有料一点
Come on, Cold, you got better material than that.

189
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:11,320
就叫“零度以下的飞来横祸”怎么样？
How about, "Chances of that are below zero?"

190
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:14,450
唉 算了
Ah, never mind.

191
00:10:14,460 --> 00:10:16,990
我能看出来我讲的这个冷笑话把你冷到了
I can see my puns leave you cold.

192
00:10:16,990 --> 00:10:18,790
冷啊
Cold.

193
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:19,990
他随你处置了 警官
He's all yours, Officer.

194
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,990
现在是时候去大都会了
Now it's off to Metropolis.

195
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,430
多谢了 闪电侠
Thanks, Flash!

196
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:25,030
嗨 你知道这些甜甜圈配啥最好不？
Hey, you know what goes good with those donuts?

197
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:26,270
你去没去过那个
You ever been to that

198
00:10:26,270 --> 00:10:28,370
在星城的兰伯特奶昔？
Lampert's Milkshakes in Star City?

199
00:10:28,370 --> 00:10:30,300
没
No.

200
00:10:34,940 --> 00:10:37,110
准备 瞄准…
Ready, aim...

201
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:39,150
发射！
Fire!

202
00:10:43,190 --> 00:10:44,890
这些机器小丑速度好快
These roboclowns are quick.

203
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:48,990
每次我来城里观光
Whenever I visit the city,

204
00:10:48,990 --> 00:10:52,330
最喜欢的就是看一场好的演出
I just love to take in a good show.

205
00:10:52,330 --> 00:10:54,930
那你肯定会喜欢我的表演
Then you're gonna love my performance as

206
00:10:54,930 --> 00:10:56,630
我演直升机
a helicopter.

207
00:11:04,070 --> 00:11:05,640
干得好，塑胶人
Well done, Plas.

208
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:09,040
真棒！好精彩的表演
Bravo! Wonderful performances.

209
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:11,510
我笑了 我哭了
I laughed, I cried.

210
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:14,550
我的机器小丑都死了
My roboclowns died.

211
00:11:16,650 --> 00:11:19,620
给你最热烈的粉丝拍张照如何？
Photo for your biggest fan?

212
00:11:19,620 --> 00:11:21,660
茄子
Say, "Cheese."

213
00:11:21,660 --> 00:11:22,690
塑胶人 不要！
Plas, no!

214
00:11:26,930 --> 00:11:30,330
这就是书里那种最老的恶作剧对吧？
That was the oldest trick in the book, wasn't it?

215
00:11:30,330 --> 00:11:33,240
你这家伙的脑子真是慢得可以
You are so gonna get it later.

216
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:38,740
我爱死他们高空摔落地面成就经典这一幕了
I love it when they fall for the classics.

217
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:41,570
哦 塑胶人
Oh, Plastic Man!

218
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:44,710
聪明倒是挺聪明，可惜脑子老是慢半拍
Always clever,but never too quick.

219
00:11:46,780 --> 00:11:48,320
闪电侠
Flash.

220
00:11:53,590 --> 00:11:54,690
哇哦
Wow.

221
00:11:54,690 --> 00:11:57,760
我想说 真的是 哇哦
I mean, really, wow.

222
00:11:59,190 --> 00:12:01,500
蝙蝠侠肯定要气炸了 他最讨厌迟到
Batman is gonna be so mad.He hates tardiness.

223
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:08,500
哦，追逐戏，我最爱追逐戏码了
Ooh, a chase scene.I love chase scenes.

224
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:14,840
回旋镖队长
Captain Boomerang.

225
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:17,110
你知道吗，你是我今天碰到的第二个
You know, you're the second captain wearing blue

226
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:18,510
穿蓝衣服的队长了
that I've run into today.

227
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:20,080
你们是组了个俱乐部还是怎么样？
You guys have a club or something?

228
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:23,480
那是 俱乐部名字叫“干翻闪电侠”
Yeah, it's the"Let's destroy Flash" club.

229
00:12:23,490 --> 00:12:24,620
呃……哦
Uh-oh.

230
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:27,650
又一发 再来一发
And another, and another.

231
00:12:27,660 --> 00:12:29,060
还有一发
And another.

232
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:32,730
哈！没打着！
Ha! Missed me!

233
00:12:32,730 --> 00:12:34,760
- 哦 真的吗？ - 是的
- Oh, did I?- Yeah, you did.

234
00:12:35,430 --> 00:12:36,630
哎呀！
Crikey!

235
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:45,240
这下回旋镖可回旋不动了
Well, that puts the boom in Boomerang.

236
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:47,010
啊？
Huh?

237
00:12:47,010 --> 00:12:48,840
我错过麻烦事警报了
I missed the trouble alert.

238
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,440
我的错 调成震动了
My bad, had it on vibrate.

239
00:12:50,450 --> 00:12:52,620
蝙蝠侠肯定气疯了
Batman is gonna be so mad.

240
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:55,780
哎呀！奶昔不错嘛
Blimey! Good shake.

241
00:13:01,660 --> 00:13:05,290
注意了 大都会旅游协会
Attention,Metropolis Board of Tourism,

242
00:13:05,290 --> 00:13:08,330
你们的旅游搞得我好无聊
I'm bored with your tourism.

243
00:13:08,330 --> 00:13:10,560
奇思妙想在哪里？哪里好玩啦？
Where's the whimsy,where's the fun?

244
00:13:10,570 --> 00:13:13,370
哼 我现在就给你们弄点好玩的
Well, I'm gonna give it to ya

245
00:13:13,370 --> 00:13:16,170
看我的好玩加农炮
with my Fun Cannon.

246
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,340
终于，
At last,

247
00:13:21,340 --> 00:13:23,610
我最大的敌人打出了他最后一张牌
my greatest foe plays his final card.

248
00:13:23,610 --> 00:13:25,980
只有我一个人能阻止他
And it's up to me alone to stop him.

249
00:13:25,980 --> 00:13:28,420
这将是我们的终极之战
This could be our end game.

250
00:13:28,420 --> 00:13:30,650
这是最后的战役 在一段很长的……
The last battle in a long...

251
00:13:30,650 --> 00:13:32,720
不好 他的武器充能好快
Impressive, his weapon charged so quickly.

252
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:35,830
他要按按钮了 没时间了 必须马上出击
He's going for the trigger. No time.Have to strike now, go!

253
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:46,470
小蝠蝠 在哥谭市里我最想念的人就是你啦
Batsy, how I've missed you in Gotham City.

254
00:13:46,470 --> 00:13:49,900
但你现在总是跟你的朋友们一起行动了
You're always off to play with your superfriends now.

255
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:53,940
所以我大老远跑到大都会来跟你们一起好好玩玩
So I came all the way to Metropolis to join the fun.

256
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:55,680
好玩的都玩完了 小丑
Fun's over, Joker.

257
00:13:55,680 --> 00:13:57,610
我已经阻止了你的计划
I foiled your plan.

258
00:13:57,610 --> 00:13:59,610
什么？哦···
What? Oh.

259
00:13:59,620 --> 00:14:03,520
你以为你的蝙蝠镖已经击溃了我的好玩加农炮了吗？
You thought your Batarang defeated my Fun Cannon?

260
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:07,560
等下 你那个按钮是干啥用的？
Wait, then what's that button for?

261
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:08,720
这个钮吗？
This button?

262
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:11,220
这是空调开关
It turns on the air conditioner.

263
00:14:11,230 --> 00:14:14,490
这个按钮才是我的好玩加农炮开炮用的
This button fires my Fun Cannon.

264
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:17,160
不！
No!

265
00:14:17,170 --> 00:14:19,440
太慢了 小蝠蝠
Too slow, Batsy.

266
00:14:32,210 --> 00:14:34,210
现在这情况看起来可不太妙
This does not look good.

267
00:14:34,220 --> 00:14:35,750
你说得对
You're right.

268
00:14:35,750 --> 00:14:37,490
这个看起来简直要笑死人了
It looks hilarious.

269
00:14:39,490 --> 00:14:41,820
谢谢 谢谢大家 我会在这里表演整整一周的
Thank you, thank you.I'll be here all week.

270
00:14:41,820 --> 00:14:45,620
实际上 我觉得我可以在这呆一辈子
In fact, I think I'll stay here forever!

271
00:14:50,930 --> 00:14:53,970
现在 如果我把这个原子
Now, if I just add this atom

272
00:14:53,970 --> 00:14:55,540
加在这个分子上
on to this molecule,

273
00:14:55,540 --> 00:14:57,740
它应该能让毒气失效
it should make the gas inert.

274
00:14:58,770 --> 00:15:01,570
搞定了！我刚刚发现了解药
Eureka!I've discovered the cure.

275
00:15:01,580 --> 00:15:04,180
现在，合成一个疫苗
Now, to synthesize a vaccine.

276
00:15:20,230 --> 00:15:22,030
我说……
I said...

277
00:15:33,710 --> 00:15:36,640
蝙蝠小丑？
Batclown?

278
00:15:36,650 --> 00:15:39,710
呃 我活已经干完了
Well, my work is done here.

279
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:48,520
啊？
Huh?

280
00:15:50,990 --> 00:15:52,790
抱歉我来晚了
Sorry I'm late.

281
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:54,460
他打败了小丑 谢谢你！
He took down the Joker! Thank you!

282
00:15:56,870 --> 00:15:58,930
什么？
What?

283
00:15:58,930 --> 00:16:00,600
谢谢 谢谢大家
Thank you, thank you.

284
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:02,340
你知道 这点活一天就搞定了
You know,it's all in a day's work.

285
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,440
喔哦 你怎么搞成这样？
Whoa! What happened to you?

286
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:08,010
你迟到的时候就会搞成这样！
This is what happens when you're late!

287
00:16:08,010 --> 00:16:09,610
我知道 非常抱歉
I know, I am so sorry.

288
00:16:09,610 --> 00:16:11,580
因为我把我的联盟警报器调到振动模式了
I had my League alert on vibrate.

289
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:14,150
然后我这一早上特别忙 又是冰冻队长又是回旋镖队长的
And then a really busy morning with Captain Cold and Captain Boomerang.

290
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:15,480
但是 嗨 我们抓到小丑了
But, hey,the Joker is captured

291
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:17,790
然后大家从衣着来看都没什么不好的地方
and everyone seems no worse for wear.

292
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:20,350
- 啊 大部分吧  - 还有星球日报
- Well, mostly...- And the Daily Planet?

293
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,790
什么？
What?

294
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:25,560
终极大楼变身准备 三 二  一！
Extreme building makeover in three, two, one!

295
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:37,100
万岁！闪电侠最棒了！
- Hurray!- Flash is the best.

296
00:16:37,110 --> 00:16:40,010
超级速度啥都能修复 跟新的一样
Super speed fixes everything.Just like new.

297
00:16:40,010 --> 00:16:41,510
你想不想让我把你也修复一下呀 蝙蝠侠？
You want me to fix you up, too, Batman?

298
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:44,010
不是啥都都能用超级速度来修复的
Not everything can be fixed with speed.

299
00:16:44,010 --> 00:16:46,550
闪电侠 蝙蝠侠想说的是
Flash, what Batman is trying to say,

300
00:16:46,550 --> 00:16:48,280
我们都是你的朋友
is that we're you're friends.

301
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:49,780
我没想说这个
That's not what I said.

302
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:53,250
我们想让你成为你能做到的最好的英雄
And we want you to be the best hero you can be.

303
00:16:53,250 --> 00:16:55,320
有时候那意味着放慢速度
Sometimes that means slowing down.

304
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:57,390
留意一下你的周围
Being aware of your surroundings.

305
00:16:57,390 --> 00:17:00,300
而且永远有一套计划
And always having a plan.

306
00:17:01,260 --> 00:17:03,460
- 闪电侠？ - 慢下来
- Flash?- Slow down.

307
00:17:03,470 --> 00:17:05,500
环境还有计划 记下了
Surroundings and plan, got it.

308
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:07,270
- 话题标签 #前瞻性行动#…… - 闪电侠？
- Hashtag proactive.- Flash?

309
00:17:07,270 --> 00:17:09,400
更新我的英雄热线 英雄Ins[Ins：美国社交网站、应用]
Updating my Hero Hotline, Herogram.

310
00:17:09,410 --> 00:17:11,470
爱英雄，英雄乌托邦和我的英雄
I-Hero, Herotopia and MyHero

311
00:17:11,470 --> 00:17:14,070
推送一下我打败小丑的消息
with my takedown of the Joker.

312
00:17:14,080 --> 00:17:16,510
哦 太感谢你们了 正义联盟
Oh, thank you, Justice League.

313
00:17:16,510 --> 00:17:19,080
没有你们我们真不知道该怎么办
We don't know what we'd do without you.

314
00:17:19,080 --> 00:17:21,710
- 嗯……- 嗯 市长 只要我是世界上速度最快的人
- Well...- Well, Mayor, as long as I'm the fastest man alive,

315
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:23,320
那你永远都不用担心
you'll never have to worry about it.

316
00:17:23,320 --> 00:17:27,090
但你才不是世界上速度最快的人
But you aren't the fastest man alive.

317
00:17:27,090 --> 00:17:28,420
你是个骗子
You're a fraud,

318
00:17:28,420 --> 00:17:30,060
就像正义联盟的其它成员一样
just like the rest of the Justice League.

319
00:17:30,060 --> 00:17:34,030
世界很快就会发现这一点
Something the world will see soon enough.

320
00:17:37,230 --> 00:17:39,530
- 那个人是谁啊 - 不知道
- Who was that?- No clue.

321
00:17:39,530 --> 00:17:41,530
我会把他找出来的
But I'm gonna find out.

322
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:42,770
闪电侠 等等
Flash, wait.

323
00:17:49,410 --> 00:17:51,650
这家伙速度还真快
Huh? This guy is seriously fast.

324
00:17:54,150 --> 00:17:56,150
你穿的是铁靴子吗？
Are you wearing iron boots?

325
00:17:56,150 --> 00:17:57,450
我知道你动作会慢一些，
I knew you would be slow,

326
00:17:57,450 --> 00:17:59,790
但我还真不知道你会慢成这样
but I didn't know you'd be this slow.

327
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:03,060
你才不可能打败我
No way you're beating me.

328
00:18:13,530 --> 00:18:15,800
这倒挺新鲜
Whoa! That's new.

329
00:18:22,910 --> 00:18:24,310
哇！
Wow!

330
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:25,610
我在哪儿？
Where am I?

331
00:18:25,610 --> 00:18:28,250
别急 你会再看见的
Don't worry,you'll see it again.

332
00:18:28,250 --> 00:18:29,550
很快
Soon.

333
00:18:37,290 --> 00:18:39,600
似曾相识啊
Deja vu. Bah.

334
00:18:41,900 --> 00:18:43,400
下一次可得记住
You'd think I'd learn by now.

335
00:18:45,130 --> 00:18:46,130
不错
Nice.

336
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:49,700
哦耶 是时候出发了！
Oh, yeah. It's go time!

337
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:52,980
- 嘿！你撞我车了！- 什么？根本不能怪我 你看看我的车
- Hey, you hit my car!- What? That ain't my fault, look at my car.

338
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,740
哥们儿 我们昨天就来过一遍了
Guys, we did this yesterday,

339
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:58,040
你俩开车真该仔细看看路
you really gotta watch where you're going.

340
00:18:58,050 --> 00:18:59,610
谢谢 闪电侠
Thanks, Flash.

341
00:18:59,610 --> 00:19:02,480
不用上学了 不用上学了
- No school.- No way. No school?

342
00:19:03,690 --> 00:19:05,280
连续两天爆胎？
Two blowouts in a row?

343
00:19:05,290 --> 00:19:07,520
听着 这是城市那边我相熟的一家轮胎店
Listen, here's the card for a tire shop I know across town.

344
00:19:07,520 --> 00:19:10,390
如果你提我名字的话他们会以超优惠的价格给你换新轮胎的
They'll give you a great deal on new tires if you mention my name.

345
00:19:10,390 --> 00:19:12,130
拜拜
- See ya.- Uh...

346
00:19:12,130 --> 00:19:13,530
谢谢 闪电侠
Thanks, Flash?

347
00:19:13,530 --> 00:19:15,130
谢谢 闪电侠
Thanks, Flash.

348
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,970
喔啊！
Whoa!

349
00:19:19,970 --> 00:19:22,100
哈 你知道不 跟昨天我们搭的那个比
Ha! You know, I like this one even better than the one

350
00:19:22,100 --> 00:19:23,140
我更喜欢今天搭的这个
we put up yesterday.

351
00:19:23,970 --> 00:19:25,010
谢啦 闪电侠！
Thanks, Flash!

352
00:19:26,180 --> 00:19:27,610
三重似曾相识
Triple deja vu.

353
00:19:27,610 --> 00:19:28,910
饿了
Oh, hungry.

354
00:19:28,910 --> 00:19:30,610
你知道有啥东西能让我的肚子感觉好一点不？
You know what would make my tummy feel better?

355
00:19:30,610 --> 00:19:32,610
再来一轮福克斯家的甜甜圈
Another round of donuts at Fox's

356
00:19:32,610 --> 00:19:34,080
而且这次我不用再操心
and this time I won't have to worry about

357
00:19:34,080 --> 00:19:36,920
冰冻队长耽误我吃饭了
Captain Cold interrupting my chowtime.

358
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:38,190
