876
00:48:58,650 --> 00:49:02,280
嗯 快跑行不通 而且命运博士说我会被考验
Well, going fast didn't work,and Fate said I'd be tested.

877
00:49:10,460 --> 00:49:13,720
这怎么起效的？
How is this working?

878
00:49:13,730 --> 00:49:18,200
我真的 真的 真的讨厌慢慢走
I really, really, really hate going slow.

879
00:49:20,300 --> 00:49:21,630
天呐
Holy moly.

880
00:49:21,630 --> 00:49:24,030
还真管用了！我做到了！
It actually worked!I did it!

881
00:49:24,040 --> 00:49:25,340
小菜一碟嘛
Piece of cake.

882
00:49:29,410 --> 00:49:30,740
日志输入编号14
Journal entry 14.

883
00:49:30,740 --> 00:49:33,650
情况变得粘乎乎毫无进展
The situation has grown sticky.

884
00:49:36,150 --> 00:49:37,880
但我必须保留我身上的智慧
But I must keep my wits about me.

885
00:49:37,880 --> 00:49:41,090
我必须要动用身边的一切可用之物来保命
I must use everything at my disposal to survive.

886
00:49:41,090 --> 00:49:43,820
我必须用到，科学！
I must use science!

887
00:49:45,630 --> 00:49:47,860
关于蛛形纲的一个小小的广为人知的假说
A little known hypothesis about arachnids

888
00:49:47,860 --> 00:49:51,230
就是他们会被闪烁的光源催眠
is that they can be hypnotized by flashing lights.

889
00:49:51,230 --> 00:49:53,230
是时候验证一下这个理论了
Time to test that theory.

890
00:49:53,230 --> 00:49:55,100
科学会赢吗？
Can science prevail?

891
00:49:55,100 --> 00:49:56,940
还是蜘蛛会取胜呢？
Will the spider be hypnotized?

892
00:49:56,940 --> 00:50:01,280
难道我将在蜘蛛体内学习它的消化过程吗？
Will I learn about spider digestion from the inside?

893
00:50:03,840 --> 00:50:05,040
有了！
Eureka!

894
00:50:09,250 --> 00:50:10,950
啊哈！
Aha!

895
00:50:10,950 --> 00:50:13,080
研究表明部分鸟类会被驯化
Studies have shown tha some birds can be tamed

896
00:50:13,090 --> 00:50:16,860
通过在后背上的某处特殊神经施加一点点压力
by applying gentle pressure to a special nerve on the back.

897
00:50:16,860 --> 00:50:20,930
这只家鸽证明了那些研究的正确性
This Columba livia domestica proves those studies correct.

898
00:50:23,230 --> 00:50:25,660
那么现在就去正义大厅吧
And now to the Hall of Justice.

899
00:50:25,670 --> 00:50:27,800
希望我来得及通知正义联盟
Hopefully, I'm in time to alert the League

900
00:50:27,800 --> 00:50:30,600
赶在逆闪造成更多破坏之前
before Reverse-Flash can do any more damage.

901
00:50:41,980 --> 00:50:43,250
哦 我懂了
Oh, I get it.

902
00:50:43,250 --> 00:50:44,880
我手机上有这个小游戏
I have this game on my phone.

903
00:50:44,880 --> 00:50:47,150
我只要想办法跳上这些板块一直跳到顶就可以了
All I have to do is ride these to the top.

904
00:50:48,420 --> 00:50:49,950
哇啊 好痛
Ow! Whoa. That hurt.

905
00:50:49,960 --> 00:50:52,520
说不定这个是某种耐力考验
Maybe this is some sort of endurance test.

906
00:50:52,530 --> 00:50:55,060
我必须要表现出我能扛得住
I just have to show I can take it.

907
00:50:57,600 --> 00:50:59,930
我扛不住啊啊啊！
I can't take it!

908
00:51:17,980 --> 00:51:22,490
留意你的周围
Be aware of your surroundings.

909
00:51:22,490 --> 00:51:24,930
我的周围？
My surroundings?

910
00:51:31,600 --> 00:51:33,700
我之前从没注意过那些平台
I never noticed those platforms before.

911
00:51:36,740 --> 00:51:40,900
哇哦 通向大门的路一直就在那里啊
Wow, the path to the door was there the whole time.

912
00:51:44,710 --> 00:51:46,610
哈！小菜一碟 柠檬……
Ha! Easy-peasy, lemon...

913
00:51:46,610 --> 00:51:49,050
还是好痛 还是好痛
Still hurts. Still hurts.

914
00:51:55,490 --> 00:51:59,220
感谢你加入我们 逆闪电
Thank you for joining us,Reverse-Flash.

915
00:51:59,230 --> 00:52:00,720
这是我的荣幸 市长
It's my pleasure, Mayor.

916
00:52:00,730 --> 00:52:02,960
能为社群服务 我十分荣幸
I serve with the pleasure of the community.

917
00:52:02,960 --> 00:52:06,930
你不会在什么私人小岛上的俱乐部别墅里看到我，不会的
You won't see me in some private island clubhouse, no.

918
00:52:06,930 --> 00:52:11,100
我就爱当人民公仆啊
I love being the servant of the people.

919
00:52:11,100 --> 00:52:12,840
你真令人敬佩
You're incredible.

920
00:52:12,840 --> 00:52:16,440
你不仅阻止了毒藤女和她那些发狂的植物
Not only did you stop Poison Ivy and her maniacal plants, you...

921
00:52:16,440 --> 00:52:18,540
我们为什么要在这鬼鬼崇崇的？
Why are we sneaking around?

922
00:52:18,550 --> 00:52:20,880
你要懂得这就是蝙蝠侠做事的风格
You know this is how Batman does things.

923
00:52:20,880 --> 00:52:22,680
我们正在暗中监视逆闪
We're spying on Reverse-Flash,

924
00:52:22,680 --> 00:52:24,780
因为蝙蝠侠觉得自己最终会给他使个绊子
because Batman thinks he'll eventually trip up

925
00:52:24,780 --> 00:52:27,420
把他真实的邪恶目的暴露人前
and reveal his true evil intentions.

926
00:52:27,420 --> 00:52:28,720
正确 钢骨
Correct, Cyborg.

927
00:52:28,720 --> 00:52:30,260
这是一次秘密侦查
This is a covert op.

928
00:52:30,260 --> 00:52:33,820
我们将会从暗影处窥探 在暗影中行动
We'll spy from the shadows,move in the shadows,

929
00:52:33,830 --> 00:52:35,030
成为……
be the...

930
00:52:35,030 --> 00:52:37,060
火风暴 把你脑袋灯关了
Firestorm,turn down your head.

931
00:52:37,060 --> 00:52:38,660
哦 抱歉
Oh. Sorry.

932
00:52:38,670 --> 00:52:41,670
我的谦逊质朴不允许我取得任何的褒奖 市长小姐
Modesty forbids me from taking such praise, Miss Mayor.

933
00:52:41,670 --> 00:52:44,500
说起哥谭市
And speaking of Gotham City,

934
00:52:44,500 --> 00:52:49,070
你知道蝙蝠侠和罗宾被巨石砸中叫什么吗？
为啥，不知道啊
- do you know what you call Batman and Robin under a rock?- Why, no.

935
00:52:49,070 --> 00:52:50,880
扁平男和罗带宾
Flatman and Ribbon.

936
00:52:53,010 --> 00:52:56,350
哦哦 还有个段子 请问钢骨什么时候换裤子？
Oh! Here's another. When does Cyborg change his pants?

937
00:52:56,350 --> 00:52:58,980
永远不换 他根本没穿裤子
Never. He's not wearing any.

938
00:53:00,350 --> 00:53:01,820
嘘……
Shh.

939
00:53:01,820 --> 00:53:04,190
我肯定每一位在家看电视的观众都会同意
As I'm sure everyone at home would agree,

940
00:53:04,190 --> 00:53:09,190
你已经让大都会和整个世界都变得更加安全
you have made Metropolis and the world a safer place.

941
00:53:09,190 --> 00:53:12,200
你作为一个超级英雄 既不要求荣誉授勋
You're a hero that never asks for accolades

942
00:53:12,200 --> 00:53:15,570
也不会穿那种很浮夸的披风之类的东西
or wears something as gaudy as a cape.

943
00:53:15,570 --> 00:53:17,130
浮夸？浮夸？
- Gaudy?
- Gaudy?

944
00:53:17,140 --> 00:53:18,570
因为这些
And for that,

945
00:53:18,570 --> 00:53:20,900
我们想要授予你一项荣誉
we'd like to honor you

946
00:53:20,910 --> 00:53:22,870
城市之匙
with the key to the city.

947
00:53:22,880 --> 00:53:25,810
感谢大家 大都会善良的居民们
Thank you,
fine citizens of Metropolis.

948
00:53:25,810 --> 00:53:29,310
我接受你们一文不值的……我是说珍贵的 礼物
I accept your paltry...I mean, precious gift.

949
00:53:30,950 --> 00:53:33,180
很快这个世界就将意识到 其实你们已经明白了
Soon the world will realize what you have already learned.

950
00:53:33,190 --> 00:53:35,890
我 逆闪电
That I, Reverse-Flash,

951
00:53:35,890 --> 00:53:39,760
是你们唯一需要的超级英雄
am the only hero you will ever need.

952
00:53:41,190 --> 00:53:42,630
不要啊 塑胶人
No, Plastic Man.

953
00:53:42,630 --> 00:53:43,730
你在支撑横梁上放太多重量了
You're putting too much weight on the support beam.

954
00:53:43,730 --> 00:53:45,670
你得……
You need to...

955
00:53:48,000 --> 00:53:51,940
这就是为什么蝙蝠侠单独行动
This is why the Batman works alone.

956
00:53:51,940 --> 00:53:53,240
哦 看呐！
Oh, look!

957
00:53:53,240 --> 00:53:55,140
是正义联盟
It's the Justice League.

958
00:53:55,140 --> 00:53:58,440
或者我应该叫你们失业者联盟？
Or should I say the Jobless League.

959
00:54:02,210 --> 00:54:04,650
悲催的是 我同意
Sadly, I agree.

960
00:54:04,650 --> 00:54:07,850
这只能说明一件事
- Huh?- This can only mean one thing.

961
00:54:07,850 --> 00:54:11,690
正义联盟现在宣布退休
The Justice League is now retired.

962
00:54:28,610 --> 00:54:30,640
迷宫？我最喜欢迷宫了
A maze?Well, I love mazes!

963
00:54:30,640 --> 00:54:33,610
它们可棒了
They're amazing.

964
00:54:33,610 --> 00:54:37,020
我快到了 我能感觉到我的力量正回来呢
I'm almost there. I can feel my powers coming back.

965
00:54:40,850 --> 00:54:43,720
嗨 几乎回复到全速了
Hey, look at that.
Almost back to full speed.

966
00:54:45,420 --> 00:54:47,660
耶！哦 不是吧
Yeah! Oh, no. Huh?

967
00:55:00,140 --> 00:55:02,510
所以我要做的就是在一片漆黑中穿过这个迷宫吗？
So all I have to do is get through the maze in the dark.

968
00:55:02,510 --> 00:55:05,680
有我的超能力 那应该不是什么问题
With my super speed back,that shouldn't be a problem.

969
00:55:10,320 --> 00:55:12,680
好吧 那确实是个问题
Okay. It's a problem!

970
00:55:12,690 --> 00:55:16,090
这个地方有什么东西一直想伤害我呢？
What is it with this place trying to hurt me?

971
00:55:16,090 --> 00:55:17,990
蝙蝠侠说什么来着？
What was it Batman said?

972
00:55:17,990 --> 00:55:19,720
总是准备一套计划 总是准备一套计划
- Always have a plan.- Always have a plan.

973
00:55:19,730 --> 00:55:22,100
好的 那么 闪电 你的计划是什么？
Okay, so, Flash,what's your plan?

974
00:55:25,100 --> 00:55:27,400
哦！我可以从高处这里提前做好计划
Oh! I can make a plan from up here.

975
00:55:27,400 --> 00:55:29,330
好了 现在我们看看
Okay. Now let's see.

976
00:55:29,340 --> 00:55:32,170
左 右 右 右 等下 不 不不不不
Left, right, right, right.Wait, no, no, no, no.

977
00:55:32,170 --> 00:55:35,570
左 右 右 右 左
Okay. Left, right, right,
right, left...

978
00:55:35,570 --> 00:55:38,040
左 右 左
Okay. Left, right, left,

979
00:55:38,040 --> 00:55:40,310
左 右 左 右 左 左
left, right, left, right,left, left,

980
00:55:40,310 --> 00:55:43,350
右 右 左 左 左 完美
right, right, left, left.Perfect.

981
00:55:43,350 --> 00:55:44,850
好了 我搞定了 我搞定了
Okay, I got it. I got it.

982
00:55:51,460 --> 00:55:52,960
最后一道门了
The final door.

983
00:55:56,130 --> 00:55:59,360
啊 拜托 我怎么才能通过这扇坚固的大门？
Aw, come on! How can I get through this solid door?

984
00:55:59,370 --> 00:56:00,730
这是个死胡同嘛！
It's a dead end!

985
00:56:01,330 --> 00:56:02,430
有趣的事实
Fun fact.

986
00:56:02,440 --> 00:56:03,730
在亚原子层面上
At the subatomic level,

987
00:56:03,740 --> 00:56:06,000
死胡同绝对不是真的死胡同
dead ends aren't really dead ends at all.

988
00:56:06,010 --> 00:56:08,270
分子之间总会存在空隙
There is always space between the molecules

989
00:56:08,270 --> 00:56:10,880
允许原子子从中间通过
that allow atoms to move between them.

990
00:56:12,650 --> 00:56:13,950
如果原子侠是对的
If the Atom is right,

991
00:56:13,950 --> 00:56:16,280
一切事物之间都有空隙的话
and there is space between everything,

992
00:56:16,280 --> 00:56:18,820
我需要做的就是像神速砖那样，
I just have to do what the speed bricks did

993
00:56:18,820 --> 00:56:21,920
把自己振动成分子状态从事物的空隙中穿过去
and vibrate my molecules to fit between them.

994
00:56:21,920 --> 00:56:25,230
嗯 来吧 一切就靠这个了
Well, here goes everything.

995
00:56:33,970 --> 00:56:36,300
我刚刚振动通过那堵墙了
I just vibrated through that wall.

996
00:56:37,440 --> 00:56:39,110
我无所不能啊！
I can do anything!

997
00:56:39,740 --> 00:56:41,070
就是这里了
That's it.

998
00:56:41,070 --> 00:56:44,110
我能感觉到它在激发出神速力
I can feel it radiating the Speed Force.

999
00:56:51,120 --> 00:56:52,480
哇哦！
Wow!

1000
00:56:52,480 --> 00:56:54,990
它是某种核心
It's some kind of nexus.

1001
00:56:59,530 --> 00:57:00,890
太惊人了！
It's amazing!

1002
00:57:00,890 --> 00:57:03,390
我终于做到了！
I've finally done it!

1003
00:57:03,400 --> 00:57:05,160
没有什么能阻止我……
Nothing can stop...

1004
00:57:09,000 --> 00:57:10,530
终于！
At last!

1005
00:57:10,540 --> 00:57:12,070
逆闪？
Reverse-Flash?

1006
00:57:12,070 --> 00:57:14,740
- 但是怎么会这样？ - 还是慢半拍，对不？
- But how?- Still too slow, aren't you?

1007
00:57:14,740 --> 00:57:16,210
时间循环
The time loop.

1008
00:57:16,210 --> 00:57:19,110
你打破了你与神速力之间的连接
You breaking your connection to the Speed Force,

1009
00:57:19,110 --> 00:57:21,380
我早知道它会引导你来到这里
I knew it would all lead you here,

1010
00:57:21,380 --> 00:57:23,110
来到神速力之核
to the Speed Force nexus.

1011
00:57:23,110 --> 00:57:26,120
而且 通过那个荒谬的障碍机关
And also, through that ridiculous obstacle course...

1012
00:57:26,120 --> 00:57:28,250
我说 你是不是在逗我？
I mean, are you kidding me?

1013
00:57:28,260 --> 00:57:29,590
多危险啊！
Dangerous!

1014
00:57:29,590 --> 00:57:33,760
所以我忽悠你为我打开这三道门
So I duped you into opening
the three doors for me.

1015
00:57:33,760 --> 00:57:36,490
恭喜你啦 失败者！
Congratulations, loser!

1016
00:57:36,500 --> 00:57:37,730
现在嘛
And now,

1017
00:57:37,730 --> 00:57:39,830
取得了神速力之核的力量
with the power of the nexus,

1018
00:57:39,830 --> 00:57:42,100
再没有什么东西能阻挡我了
nothing can stand in my way.

1019
00:57:48,710 --> 00:57:50,110
这力量
The power!

1020
00:57:50,110 --> 00:57:54,750
感觉 感觉像是连喝了52杯奶昔
It's... It's like drinking 52 milkshakes

1021
00:57:54,750 --> 00:57:57,510
又吃下整整一大袋果冻软糖！
and eating a bag of jelly beans!

1022
00:57:57,520 --> 00:58:00,380
精神百倍！
Invigorating!

1023
00:58:00,390 --> 00:58:03,320
神速力之核是我的！我努力赢来的！
The nexus is mine!I earned it!

1024
00:58:04,560 --> 00:58:07,090
祝你们好运吧，你们将被永远困在这里
Good luck being trapped here for all eternity.

1025
00:58:18,870 --> 00:58:21,240
我真没法相信我们要退休了
I can't believe that we're retiring.

1026
00:58:21,240 --> 00:58:23,270
我是说 我们将何去何从啊？
I mean,where do we go from here?

1027
00:58:23,280 --> 00:58:25,580
英雄们 钢骨 永远不要放弃希望
Heroes, Cyborg,never give up hope.

1028
00:58:25,580 --> 00:58:29,480
而我 还没有放弃调查逆闪
And I haven't given up investigating Reverse-Flash.

1029
00:58:29,480 --> 00:58:32,620
哦 巨星陨落啊
Oh, how the mighty have fallen.

1030
00:58:32,620 --> 00:58:34,850
一度辉煌的正义联盟
The once great Justice League

1031
00:58:34,850 --> 00:58:37,820
被迫退休
forced into retirement.

1032
00:58:37,820 --> 00:58:40,120
面对现实吧 超级狗熊们
Face it, super zeroes,

1033
00:58:40,130 --> 00:58:41,730
你们已经是昨日黄花了
you're yesterday's news!

1034
00:58:41,730 --> 00:58:46,260
快节奏的今日世界需要一个青出于蓝的英雄人物
Today's fast-paced world needs a hero like yours truly.

1035
00:58:46,260 --> 00:58:49,500
还得谢谢你们的老朋友 闪电侠
And thanks to your old pal, Flash,

1036
00:58:49,500 --> 00:58:53,000
未来的史册上将只会记得我
future history books will know only me

1037
00:58:53,010 --> 00:58:55,240
是地球上最伟大的冠军战士
as Earth's greatest champion.

1038
00:58:55,240 --> 00:58:56,310
瞧着吧
Watch.

1039
00:58:56,880 --> 00:58:58,780
快看外面！
Look, outside!

1040
00:59:12,660 --> 00:59:13,860
他在干什么？
What is he doing?

1041
00:59:13,860 --> 00:59:15,530
他在用墙来困住我们
He's walling us in.

1042
00:59:15,530 --> 00:59:18,060
他肯定对我的超级力量一无所知
He must not be aware of my super strength.

1043
00:59:18,060 --> 00:59:20,300
对我的嬗变能力也一无所知
Or my ability to transform matter.

1044
00:59:29,640 --> 00:59:30,910
我来得太晚了！
I'm too late!

1045
00:59:34,750 --> 00:59:36,680
那是什么材料筑成的啊？
What kind of material is that?

1046
00:59:36,680 --> 00:59:38,420
肯定不是寻常的种类
Not the normal kind.

1047
00:59:38,420 --> 00:59:41,850
我的扫描仪显示这些砖块正在以令人难以置信的速度在移动
My scanners indicate these bricks are moving at an incredible speed.

1048
00:59:41,860 --> 00:59:43,120
它们放射出的动力学能量
The kinetic energy they're putting off

1049
00:59:43,120 --> 00:59:45,560
足以抵消我们所有的超能力
is enough to counteract any of our powers.

1050
00:59:45,560 --> 00:59:48,130
你说得太对了，钢骨
Right you are, Cybore.

1051
00:59:48,130 --> 00:59:52,230
这些是来自神速力之地的神速砖
Those are speed bricks from the Speed Force Zone.

1052
00:59:52,230 --> 00:59:54,230
只有我一个人觉得那像是瞎编的吗？
Does that sound made-up to anyone else?

1053
00:59:54,230 --> 00:59:56,230
享受你们余下的几天吧
Enjoy the rest of your days

1054
00:59:56,230 --> 00:59:58,900
困在你们小小的俱乐部别墅里
trapped inside your little clubhouse.

1055
00:59:58,900 --> 01:00:00,640
哦 还有件事
Oh, one more thing.

1056
01:00:00,640 --> 01:00:03,440
我已经启动了你们正义大厅的安全系统
I've activated your Hall of Justice security systems

1057
01:00:03,440 --> 01:00:05,240
并且装备了反攻装置
and equipped them with countermeasures

1058
01:00:05,240 --> 01:00:07,580
专门针对你们的超能力
for each of your powers.

1059
01:00:07,580 --> 01:00:11,580
所以你们在里面可要小心一点哟
So you might wanna be careful in there.

1060
01:00:11,590 --> 01:00:14,590
毁灭 毁灭
Destroy. Destroy.{\r

1061
01:00:14,590 --> 01:00:16,750
不是吧
Not my cybots!

1062
01:00:16,760 --> 01:00:17,950
你这个禽兽
You monster.

1063
01:00:17,960 --> 01:00:19,520
我们怎么办？
What do we do?

1064
01:00:19,530 --> 01:00:22,090
对抗我设计的最强大的安保系统？
Against the most powerful security system I've ever devised?

1065
01:00:22,660 --> 01:00:23,990
我们跑
We run.

1066
01:00:27,330 --> 01:00:29,700
我怎么会这么蠢啊
How could I have bee so stupid?

1067
01:00:29,700 --> 01:00:33,570
每一步我都没逃出逆闪的掌心
At every step, I've played into the Reverse-Flash's hand.

1068
01:00:33,570 --> 01:00:34,900
他抢走了我的超能力
He took away my powers.

1069
01:00:34,910 --> 01:00:37,040
他抢走了我的朋友
He took away my friends.

1070
01:00:37,040 --> 01:00:40,510
哦 我只想回家
Oh, I just wanna go home.

1071
01:00:47,190 --> 01:00:49,290
它在振动 就好像……
It's vibrating, like...

1072
01:00:49,290 --> 01:00:51,920
就好像神速力在它们里面一样
Like they have the Speed Force inside of them.

1073
01:00:52,490 --> 01:00:53,490
我有个计划了
I have a plan.

1074
01:00:56,660 --> 01:00:57,800
不错
Not bad.

1075
01:00:57,800 --> 01:00:59,530
相当不错
Not bad at all.

1076
01:00:59,530 --> 01:01:01,900
现在来看下这些神速砖有多厉害
Now let's see what these speed bricks can do.

1077
01:01:02,800 --> 01:01:04,470
喔啊！
Whoa!

1078
01:01:21,150 --> 01:01:22,490
我所有的努力
All my hard work,

1079
01:01:22,490 --> 01:01:24,990
所有的尝试和磨难
all the trials and tribulations,

1080
01:01:24,990 --> 01:01:27,460
一无所得
for nothing.

1081
01:01:31,200 --> 01:01:34,130
超级宠物！哈！
The Super-Pets! Huh.

1082
01:01:34,130 --> 01:01:36,130
逆闪搞出这么大乱子
All this trouble with Reverse-Flash

1083
01:01:36,130 --> 01:01:39,100
他们居然只是在挖坑！
and they're just digging a hole!

1084
01:01:39,110 --> 01:01:40,770
在墙根底下挖
Under the wall.

1085
01:01:40,770 --> 01:01:42,770
当然了！太机智了！
Of course! Brilliant!

1086
01:01:42,780 --> 01:01:45,480
嗨 哥们儿 等等我！
Hey, guys, wait for me!

1087
01:01:49,580 --> 01:01:51,020
钢骨的实验室
Cyborg's laboratory.

1088
01:01:51,680 --> 01:01:53,280
好样的 兄弟们
Great job, gang.

1089
01:01:53,290 --> 01:01:56,220
现在我可以用钢骨的工具把我的缩身腰带修好
Now I can use Cyborg's tools to repair my shrinking belt

1090
01:01:56,220 --> 01:01:58,290
然后变回正常大小
and return to normal size.

1091
01:01:58,290 --> 01:02:01,460
嗨
Hey.

1092
01:02:01,460 --> 01:02:03,230
我已经搜集到足够的信息了
Well, I've collected enough data.

1093
01:02:03,230 --> 01:02:05,100
你们俩到底也不是太差劲嘛
You guys aren't so bad after all.

1094
01:02:05,100 --> 01:02:06,360
警报！警报！
Alert! Alert!

1095
01:02:06,360 --> 01:02:08,300
你们必须被清除
You must be eliminated.

1096
01:02:14,840 --> 01:02:16,610
太神奇了
Fascinating.

1097
01:02:16,610 --> 01:02:18,010
绿灯侠也有一个宠物
Green Lantern has a pet,

1098
01:02:18,010 --> 01:02:20,340
而且还是个晃着圆尾巴的松鼠？
and he's a ring-wielding squirrel?

1099
01:02:20,350 --> 01:02:22,710
嗨 你喊谁宠物呢？
Hey! Who you calling pet,short stack?

1100
01:02:22,710 --> 01:02:23,980
你会说话啊？
You can talk?

1101
01:02:23,980 --> 01:02:26,450
废话 因为我才不是什么松鼠
Yeah, because I ain't no squirrel.

1102
01:02:26,450 --> 01:02:27,690
我叫大B
Name's B'dg.

1103
01:02:27,690 --> 01:02:29,250
我是从另一个星球来的
I'm from another planet

1104
01:02:29,260 --> 01:02:32,960
我们星球上的人好死不死恰好长得有点像你们的松鼠
of people that happen to loosely resemble your squirrels.

1105
01:02:32,960 --> 01:02:35,890
我明白了 嗯 好有道理
I see. Well, that makes perfect sense.

1106
01:02:35,900 --> 01:02:38,330
能获得您的认可我真是开心
Oh, I'm so glad you approve.

1107
01:02:38,330 --> 01:02:40,560
我的好兄弟大A从这里发出了一个警报
My buddy Ace here sent down an alert.

1108
01:02:40,570 --> 01:02:41,570
我来猜猜哈，
Let me guess,

1109
01:02:41,570 --> 01:02:43,670
正义联盟有危险了？
the Justice League is in trouble?

1110
01:02:43,670 --> 01:02:45,030
旺旺
Bark.

1111
01:02:45,040 --> 01:02:46,340
惯例如此啊
As per usual.

1112
01:02:46,340 --> 01:02:50,070
嗯 我们去救他们吧 再一次
Well, let's go rescue them, again.

1113
01:02:50,080 --> 01:02:51,540
有没有谁能解释一下
Can someone explain

1114
01:02:51,540 --> 01:02:54,240
逆闪是怎么控制我的钢骨机器人的？
how Reverse-Flash can turn my cybots against us?

1115
01:02:54,250 --> 01:02:56,710
他的超级速度不知怎么的被增强了
Somehow his speed power's been supercharged.

1116
01:02:56,720 --> 01:02:59,120
是时候撤退然后想出个计划来了
Time to fall back and form a plan.

1117
01:02:59,120 --> 01:03:02,220
已经被逼到悬崖边上了 我真希望闪电侠在这里
By the toenails of Tartarus,I wish that Flash was here.

1118
01:03:03,760 --> 01:03:06,160
嗨 各位 在这边！
Hey, guys, over here!

1119
01:03:06,160 --> 01:03:09,260
清除 清除
Eliminate. Eliminate.

1120
01:03:09,260 --> 01:03:11,060
多谢及时出手相救啊 伙计们
Thanks forthe quick save, gang.

1121
01:03:13,030 --> 01:03:14,400
我不可能在这顶一辈子
I can't hold them off forever.

1122
01:03:14,400 --> 01:03:16,130
我们得想办法找路离开这里
We need to find a way out of here.

1123
01:03:16,130 --> 01:03:17,970
离开这个天堂吗？
And leave this paradise?

1124
01:03:17,970 --> 01:03:19,370
谁会知道海王的卧室
Who knew Aquaman's bedroom

1125
01:03:19,370 --> 01:03:21,870
简直就是星球最佳日间水疗浴场呢
was like the best day spa in the planet?

1126
01:03:21,870 --> 01:03:23,910
噢，哈！
Ooh, ha!

1127
01:03:23,910 --> 01:03:26,380
当然了，海之王就是应该有张水床
Of course, the king of the sea has a waterbed.

1128
01:03:26,380 --> 01:03:28,340
- 塑胶！- 各位？
- Plas!- Guys?

1129
01:03:28,350 --> 01:03:31,720
挺住啊 超人 超级宠物们有个计划
Hang in there, Superman.The Super-Pets have a plan.

1130
01:03:31,720 --> 01:03:33,020
人家不是宠物
Not a pet.

1131
01:03:36,990 --> 01:03:39,620
我相信他们在呼唤什么人
I believe they're calling someone.

1132
01:03:39,630 --> 01:03:41,090
你现在都会说狗语了？
You speak dog now?

1133
01:03:41,090 --> 01:03:44,260
不会啊，我只是理解我的朋友们
No, I just understand my friends.

1134
01:03:49,070 --> 01:03:50,200
一只海马？
A seahorse?

1135
01:03:50,200 --> 01:03:52,370
又来一只超级宠物？
Yet another Super-Pet?

1136
01:03:52,370 --> 01:03:54,340
再说一次 人家不是宠物
Again, not a pet.

1137
01:03:54,340 --> 01:03:55,640
这是暴风
This is Storm.

1138
01:03:55,640 --> 01:03:57,510
他从前与海王并肩战斗
He's fought alongside Aquaman before,

1139
01:03:57,510 --> 01:04:00,140
所以他总是愿意伸出援手
so he's always ready to lend a hand.

1140
01:04:00,150 --> 01:04:02,310
或者是援鳍 哈？
Or a fin. Huh?

1141
01:04:02,320 --> 01:04:04,210
诸位？
Guys?

1142
01:04:04,220 --> 01:04:06,450
超人 保持超级
Superman, stay super.

1143
01:04:06,450 --> 01:04:08,550
暴风 我们需要你带我们下海
Storm, we'll need you to lead us out to sea

1144
01:04:08,550 --> 01:04:10,790
穿过你来时经过的海底隧道
through the ocean tunnel you came from.

1145
01:04:10,790 --> 01:04:12,860
但首先 我们需要个交通工具
But first,we'll need a vehicle.

1146
01:04:12,860 --> 01:04:14,760
潜水艇怎么样？
How about a sub?

1147
01:04:14,760 --> 01:04:18,090
搞懂笑点没？一个潜水艇三明治 哈哈哈
Get it?A submarine sandwich.

1148
01:04:18,100 --> 01:04:20,170
抱歉……那个可以用
- Sorry...- That'll work.

1149
01:04:20,830 --> 01:04:22,570
又来了
Aw! Not again.

1150
01:04:31,580 --> 01:04:34,510
一个超级大小的潜水艇准备行动
One supersized sub ready for action.

1151
01:04:34,510 --> 01:04:36,410
诸位！我们走吧，超人！
- Guys!- Let's go, Superman.

1152
01:04:36,420 --> 01:04:37,780
是啊 你在那里挡啥呢？
Yeah, what's the hold-up?

1153
01:04:37,780 --> 01:04:41,650
清除 清除
Eliminate. Eliminate.

1154
01:04:41,650 --> 01:04:45,290
清除……哦，多可爱的小房间呐
Eliminate...Oh, my, what a lovely room.

1155
01:04:46,160 --> 01:04:49,190
暴风 去蝙蝠洞
Storm, to the Batcave.

1156
01:04:53,500 --> 01:04:55,670
“星球日报”
The Daily Planet,

1157
01:04:55,670 --> 01:05:00,270
很快就要被更名为逆闪星球了
soon to be renamed the Reverse-Flash Planet.

1158
01:05:00,270 --> 01:05:02,040
还有这个完美的天线
And the perfect antenna

1159
01:05:02,040 --> 01:05:05,680
可以把我的个人宣言广播到世界的每一个角落
to broadcast my manifesto across the world!

1160
01:05:06,550 --> 01:05:08,480
你们好啊 地球！
Hello, planet Earth!

1161
01:05:08,480 --> 01:05:13,020
是我 一直以来最受喜爱的超级英雄
It's me, the most beloved superhero of all time,

1162
01:05:13,020 --> 01:05:14,590
逆闪电
Reverse-Flash.

1163
01:05:14,590 --> 01:05:15,720
哦！
Ooh!

1164
01:05:15,720 --> 01:05:18,990
逆闪电呀 我超爱他的
The Reverse-Flash.I love him.

1165
01:05:18,990 --> 01:05:21,560
现在 我已经打破了充满罪恶的旧世界
Now that I've rid the world of crime,

1166
01:05:21,560 --> 01:05:25,430
我觉得是你们回报一下老逆闪的时候了
I think it's time for you to repay old R.F.

1167
01:05:25,430 --> 01:05:27,530
因为他仁慈的慷慨
for his kind generosity.

1168
01:05:27,530 --> 01:05:31,300
所以我命令每一个人都要到
That's why I'm ordering everyone to report

1169
01:05:31,300 --> 01:05:33,640
我的逆闪电指挥中心来向我汇报
to my Reverse-Flash command centers.

1170
01:05:33,640 --> 01:05:38,040
在那里 你们会接到指示 由我 你们的新主宰者
There, you'll be given orders on what I, your new ruler,

1171
01:05:38,040 --> 01:05:41,210
告诉你们我想让你们做什么 听起来是不是很棒？
would like you to do.Doesn't that sound wonderful?

1172
01:05:41,210 --> 01:05:44,980
没教养的猴崽子 我早就知道他不安好心
Cheeky monkey, I always knew he was rotten.

1173
01:05:44,980 --> 01:05:46,520
现在赶紧的！
Now hurry!

1174
01:05:46,520 --> 01:05:49,120
你们不想让我像对付正义联盟一样
You don't want what I did to the Justice League

1175
01:05:49,120 --> 01:05:53,260
对付你们吧
to happen to you.

1176
01:05:53,260 --> 01:05:56,930
他的能力提升了以后 我们中的任何人都不是他的对手了
With his increased powers, none of us are any match for him.

1177
01:06:00,100 --> 01:06:03,170
哦！我到处找你们大家 现在听我说
Ah! I've been looking everywhere for you guys. Now listen,

1178
01:06:03,170 --> 01:06:05,640
我知道你们多半还在为那些恶作剧生我的气
I know you're probably still mad at me for those pranks,

1179
01:06:05,640 --> 01:06:07,770
但是问题是 它不是我干的
but the thing is,it wasn't me.

1180
01:06:07,770 --> 01:06:09,640
它是这个骗人 邪恶 下流的
It was this cheating,evil, dirty,

1181
01:06:09,640 --> 01:06:12,180
长着一张蠢脸的冒名顶替的家伙干的 他从未来穿越回来的 名字叫……
doofus-faced imposter from the future named...

1182
01:06:12,180 --> 01:06:14,280
逆闪电
Reverse-Flash.

1183
01:06:14,280 --> 01:06:16,780
等下 你们知道他在冒充我？
Wait. You knew he was impersonating me?

1184
01:06:16,780 --> 01:06:20,150
不 我们不知道 一开始不知道
No, we didn't.Not at first.

1185
01:06:20,150 --> 01:06:21,920
但是有三条线索
But there were three clues.

1186
01:06:21,920 --> 01:06:24,090
你神秘兮兮的时间循环麻烦
Your mysterious time loop trouble.

1187
01:06:24,090 --> 01:06:26,690
你对孩子式幼稚的恶作剧突如其来的兴趣
Your sudden interest in childish pranks.

1188
01:06:26,690 --> 01:06:30,460
对我们说起的恶作剧矢口否认，又丧失了超能力
A sudden denial of said pranks and loss of powers.

1189
01:06:30,460 --> 01:06:33,630
你不同寻常的行为举止让我相信通过某种方法
Your unusual behavior patterns led me to believe that somehow,

1190
01:06:33,630 --> 01:06:35,770
某种途径 某个人 某个地方
some way, someone,somewhere,

1191
01:06:35,770 --> 01:06:38,540
为了某个不可告人的目的陷害你
was framing you for some unknown purpose.

1192
01:06:38,540 --> 01:06:42,310
所以 你炒我鱿鱼是为了引出逆闪？
So, you fired me to flush out the Reverse-Flash?

1193
01:06:42,310 --> 01:06:44,270
一点也不错 蝙蝠侠早就知道
Exactly.Batman knew that

1194
01:06:44,280 --> 01:06:46,010
一旦他达到了他的邪恶目的
once he accomplished his evil goals

1195
01:06:46,010 --> 01:06:47,510
他就会自己暴露大家面前
he'd reveal himself to you.

1196
01:06:47,510 --> 01:06:49,880
所以当他自曝身份的时候我就在那里
That's why I was gonna be there when he did.

1197
01:06:49,880 --> 01:06:51,580
我缩小以后落在你的肩膀上
I shrunk down onto your shoulder

1198
01:06:51,580 --> 01:06:53,280
本打算回来向联盟报告
and was going to report back to the League

1199
01:06:53,290 --> 01:06:56,050
但是反闪的手铐害我电路短路了
until Reverse-Flash's shackle shorted out my circuits,

1200
01:06:56,050 --> 01:06:58,720
所以我一直困在缩小模式里
which kept me stuck in shrink mode.

1201
01:06:58,720 --> 01:07:01,530
那就是说你们从来没有真正的放弃我
Then that means you guys never really gave up on me.

1202
01:07:01,530 --> 01:07:03,030
当然没有啦
Of course not.

1203
01:07:03,030 --> 01:07:04,630
我们是超级伙伴嘛 伙计
We're superfriends, man.

1204
01:07:04,630 --> 01:07:06,660
骗了你真是非常对不起 闪电侠
We were sorry to deceive you, Flash.

1205
01:07:06,670 --> 01:07:09,100
我们只有这一个办法帮你摆脱麻烦
It was our only play to get you out of trouble.

1206
01:07:09,100 --> 01:07:11,430
谢谢你们 这里的每一个人
Thank you, everyone.

1207
01:07:11,440 --> 01:07:13,270
是啊 真是暖心一刻啊
Yeah, yeah,real heartwarming.

1208
01:07:13,270 --> 01:07:15,940
现在 轮到我帮大家摆脱麻烦了
And now, it's my turn to get us all out of trouble.

1209
01:07:15,940 --> 01:07:18,470
我们可以用这些来阻止逆闪
We can stop the Reverse-Flash with these.

1210
01:07:18,480 --> 01:07:19,940
神速砖
Speed Force bricks.

1211
01:07:19,950 --> 01:07:21,680
而且我们可以用我神速车上的这些砖
And we can use the bricks from my speed machine

1212
01:07:21,680 --> 01:07:23,380
来给我们其它的交通工具充满能量
to superpower our other vehicles.

1213
01:07:23,380 --> 01:07:26,680
给我们所有人足够快的速度来追上逆闪
Giving us all enough speed to keep up with Reverse-Flash.

1214
01:07:26,690 --> 01:07:29,350
嗯 我还没拿回我的超能力呢 神奇女侠
Well, I don't have my speed powers back yet, Wonder Woman,

1215
01:07:29,360 --> 01:07:31,420
但是我有个更好的东西
but I have something better.

1216
01:07:31,420 --> 01:07:33,030
我有一个计划
I have a plan.

1217
01:07:35,160 --> 01:07:37,760
告诉他们所有人 你们今天建造的地标
Tell them all, the landmarks you build today

1218
01:07:37,760 --> 01:07:41,760
将会使我的英名万古长青
will glorify my name tomorrow and for all eternity.

1219
01:07:41,770 --> 01:07:43,470
看呐 是正义联盟
Look, it's the Justice League!

1220
01:07:43,470 --> 01:07:47,070
历史将铭记 世界上速度最快的人永远都是……
History will know the fastest man alive was always...

1221
01:07:58,220 --> 01:07:59,580
万岁!
Hurray!

1222
01:07:59,590 --> 01:08:02,320
嗨 你们大家！我们不打算退休了！
Hey, everybody!We're not retired anymore!

1223
01:08:02,320 --> 01:08:03,890
正义联盟回归
The Justice League is back.

1224
01:08:03,890 --> 01:08:06,960
黑暗骑士归来
- And the Dark Knight returns. - Bark.

1225
01:08:06,960 --> 01:08:10,090
这么说你们从正义大厅里逃出来了
So you've escaped the Hall of Justice

1226
01:08:10,100 --> 01:08:13,430
你们的宠物们帮的忙 毫无疑问
with help from your pets,no doubt.

1227
01:08:13,430 --> 01:08:16,130
我希望你们能享受此刻的自由
I hope you enjoyed your freedom,

1228
01:08:16,130 --> 01:08:19,600
因为它将是你们临终前看到的最后一件事了
because it will be the last thing you ever see.

1229
01:08:19,600 --> 01:08:21,670
神速砖能量开启
Powering on the speed bricks.

1230
01:08:24,480 --> 01:08:26,710
哦哦 痒痒的！
Tickles!

1231
01:08:31,480 --> 01:08:33,250
哇啊！看那边！
Whoa! Look at that!

1232
01:08:33,250 --> 01:08:35,750
看起来好像一切都静止了
It looks like everything just stopped.

1233
01:08:35,750 --> 01:08:38,860
怪不得闪电侠总是动作那么快
No wonder the Flash is always moving so fast.

1234
01:08:38,860 --> 01:08:41,830
生活在这么一个慢吞吞的世界里肯定很无聊
It must be boring to live in a world going so slow.

1235
01:08:41,830 --> 01:08:43,830
如果我们早知道他的世界是这样的
If we'd known it was like this,

1236
01:08:43,830 --> 01:08:45,760
那我们真该对他再耐心点
we might have been more patient with him.

1237
01:08:45,760 --> 01:08:48,260
学到了宝贵的一课 队员们 打起精神来
Lesson learned, team.Look alive.

1238
01:08:48,270 --> 01:08:52,500
你用什么办法获得了神速力？
Somehow you've gained the power of the Speed Force.

1239
01:08:52,510 --> 01:08:55,940
不要紧 我还是比你们所有人都要快
No matter. I'm still faster than all of you.

1240
01:08:55,940 --> 01:08:58,440
调虎离山 散开！
Evasive maneuvers.Split up.

1241
01:09:01,710 --> 01:09:04,410
你们仍然不是神速力之核的对手
You're still no match for the nexus.

1242
01:09:04,420 --> 01:09:06,620
我动作可以快到可以
I can move so fast I can seem to be

1243
01:09:06,620 --> 01:09:08,450
同时出现在五个地方
in five different places at the same time.

1244
01:09:08,450 --> 01:09:11,090
而且我可以搞定你们所有人 一劳永逸！
And I can take care of all of you, once and for all!

1245
01:09:16,860 --> 01:09:19,070
- 准备好了吗 大B？- 当然
- Ready, B'dg?- You bet.

1246
01:09:23,200 --> 01:09:26,540
我的神速砖正在返回神速力之地
My bricks are returning to the Speed Force Zone!

1247
01:09:27,270 --> 01:09:29,510
不！
No!

1248
01:09:29,510 --> 01:09:30,970
看起来闪电侠是对的
Looks like the Flash was right.

1249
01:09:30,980 --> 01:09:32,840
神速砖给了我们的飞行器
The speed bricks have given our vehicles

1250
01:09:32,850 --> 01:09:35,250
摧毁这些雕像的能力
the ability to destroy those statues.

1251
01:09:35,250 --> 01:09:36,620
拿下它 伙计们！
Go get 'em, gang!

1252
01:09:47,230 --> 01:09:49,560
目标锁定 开火！
- Target locked.- Fire!

1253
01:09:49,560 --> 01:09:51,200
炸没喽！
It's away!

1254
01:10:10,450 --> 01:10:12,820
不！
No!

1255
01:10:12,820 --> 01:10:15,080
我不知道你那些神速砖是怎么得来的
I don't know how you got those speed bricks

1256
01:10:15,090 --> 01:10:16,590
但是你的计划失败了
but your plan failed.

1257
01:10:16,590 --> 01:10:18,120
我的力量强大到
I'm powerful enough

1258
01:10:18,120 --> 01:10:20,390
不管你们在哪 都能击败正义联盟
to beat the Justice League,no matter where you are!

1259
01:10:20,390 --> 01:10:21,990
我们可没打算跟你打
We weren't trying to beat you.

1260
01:10:21,990 --> 01:10:24,060
我们只是想分散你的注意力
We were trying to distract you.

1261
01:10:24,060 --> 01:10:25,200
什么？
What?

1262
01:10:42,210 --> 01:10:44,010
这不可能 你是怎么……
Impossible. How did you...

1263
01:10:44,020 --> 01:10:45,620
在神速力之地的那些考验
The trials in the Speed Force Zone

1264
01:10:45,620 --> 01:10:47,280
不只是为了看看我是不是够资格
weren't just there to see if I was worthy,

1265
01:10:47,290 --> 01:10:49,450
那些考验是为了教导我一些东西
they were there to teach me something.

1266
01:10:49,450 --> 01:10:52,420
一些如果你花点时间自己去通关就会搞明白的事
Something you would have known if you took the time to go through them.

1267
01:10:52,430 --> 01:10:53,790
说够了吧！
Enough of this!

1268
01:10:53,790 --> 01:10:55,890
我身上还有足够的神速之核的能量
I still have enough of the nexus energy

1269
01:10:55,890 --> 01:10:58,090
可以打败像你这样的人
to defeat the likes of you.

1270
01:11:12,340 --> 01:11:15,280
好强的力量！
So much power!

1271
01:11:15,280 --> 01:11:18,180
这些力量本该是我的才对！
Which is rightfully mine!

1272
01:11:18,180 --> 01:11:21,550
我出现在你面前之前 你根本都不知道神速力是什么
You didn't even know what the Speed Force was until I showed up.

1273
01:11:21,550 --> 01:11:24,960
你凭什么以为你现在知道得足够多可以打败我？
What makes you think you know enough about it now to defeat me?

1274
01:11:24,960 --> 01:11:27,460
只有一个办法能找出答案了
Only one way to find out.

1275
01:11:28,930 --> 01:11:30,930
你永远打不赢我的 闪电侠
You'll never beat me, Flash.

1276
01:11:32,660 --> 01:11:35,100
我才是掌握了神速力的大师
I'm the master of the Speed Force!

1277
01:11:35,100 --> 01:11:37,370
真的吗？一个大师级人物应该有个计划的吧？
Really? Wouldn't a master have a plan

1278
01:11:37,370 --> 01:11:39,130
所以他没被绊倒啊？
so he doesn't get tripped up?

1279
01:11:40,470 --> 01:11:41,870
我猜是没有
Guess not.

1280
01:11:45,640 --> 01:11:48,580
你看起来很累嘛 也许你应该放慢速度
You're looking tired. Maybe you should slow down.

1281
01:11:48,580 --> 01:11:50,510
- 不！- 好啊
- No!- Okay.

1282
01:11:50,520 --> 01:11:52,150
什么？
What?

1283
01:11:55,420 --> 01:11:57,190
很疼 对吧？
- Hurts, doesn't it?- Huh?

1284
01:11:57,190 --> 01:11:59,660
留意周围 神速力大师
Way to be aware of your surroundings, Speed Force master.

1285
01:11:59,660 --> 01:12:02,390
也许你今天会赢
You may have won today,

1286
01:12:02,390 --> 01:12:03,960
但是我可以回到过去
but I'll travel back in time

1287
01:12:03,960 --> 01:12:06,130
阻止你拿到神速力之核
and stop you from getting the nexus.

1288
01:12:07,630 --> 01:12:09,230
我觉得你已经没有足够的力量了 逆闪
I don't think you have enough steam, R.F.

1289
01:12:09,230 --> 01:12:11,970
看起来你最后的神速力核之力也用完了
It looks like the last of the nexus energy is gone.

1290
01:12:11,970 --> 01:12:15,040
没有它 你根本就不够快
Without it,you're just not fast enough.

1291
01:12:15,040 --> 01:12:18,410
不够快？我是世界上速度最快的人！
Fast enough?I'm the fastest man alive!

1292
01:12:18,410 --> 01:12:19,740
就是我！
I am!

1293
01:12:19,750 --> 01:12:21,010
证明给我看
Prove it.

1294
01:12:27,650 --> 01:12:29,020
快点啊 逆闪
- Come on, R.F.- Huh?

1295
01:12:29,020 --> 01:12:32,520
你可以跑得更快的
You can go faster than that.

1296
01:12:32,520 --> 01:12:35,130
真的吗？你就这点本事了？
Really? That's all you've got?

1297
01:12:43,400 --> 01:12:44,600
什么？
What?

1298
01:12:48,370 --> 01:12:50,610
手铐不可能锁得住我
Handcuffs can't hold me.

1299
01:12:50,610 --> 01:12:52,740
我只要……
All I have to do is...

1300
01:12:52,740 --> 01:12:55,680
怎么回事？
Huh? What?

1301
01:12:56,350 --> 01:12:58,280
我的超能力
My powers.

1302
01:12:58,280 --> 01:13:01,080
啧啧啧 看起来有人和神速力之间的连接断掉了
Uh-uh-uh. Looks like someone broke his connection to the Speed Force.

1303
01:13:01,090 --> 01:13:02,390
啧啧
Tsk, tsk.

1304
01:13:02,390 --> 01:13:04,350
你应该放慢速度
You should have slowed down.

1305
01:13:04,360 --> 01:13:07,690
你 你骗我！
You! You tricked me!

1306
01:13:07,690 --> 01:13:10,460
我只是执行我的计划而已
No, no.I just executed my plan.

1307
01:13:10,460 --> 01:13:12,160
你跑不了的！
You won't get away with this!

1308
01:13:12,160 --> 01:13:13,600
我会回来的！
I'll come back!

1309
01:13:13,600 --> 01:13:16,670
不好意思 你讲话这么慢我听不懂你在说什么
Sorry. I... I can't understand when you're talking so slow.

1310
01:13:27,650 --> 01:13:29,010
妈妈
Mummy.

1311
01:13:32,050 --> 01:13:33,550
嗯 我们不会有什么麻烦事儿了
Well, we won't have any trouble

1312
01:13:33,550 --> 01:13:35,050
逆闪出事以后能消停好一阵子
from Reverse-Flash for a while.

1313
01:13:35,050 --> 01:13:37,750
- 那个神速之核怎么办？- 什么怎么办？
- What about the nexus thingy?- What about it?

1314
01:13:37,760 --> 01:13:39,120
拥有那样的力量
With power like that,

1315
01:13:39,130 --> 01:13:42,330
你可以把从此以后所有的超级英雄的活都干了
you could do the job of every hero forever.

1316
01:13:42,330 --> 01:13:45,130
看起来正义联盟还是在退休状态啊
Looks like the Justice League is still retired.

1317
01:13:46,400 --> 01:13:47,660
不
No.

1318
01:13:47,670 --> 01:13:49,530
没人应该拥有这样的力量
No one should have this much power.

1319
01:14:03,220 --> 01:14:04,180
你……
You...

1320
01:14:04,180 --> 01:14:06,280
你放弃了那样的力量
You gave up all that speed.

1321
01:14:06,680 --> 01:14:07,950
为什么呢？
But why?

1322
01:14:07,950 --> 01:14:10,150
嗯 最后我发现放慢速度
Well, it turns out that slowing down

1323
01:14:10,150 --> 01:14:12,250
才是打败逆闪的最佳途径
was the best way to defeat Reverse-Flash.

1324
01:14:12,260 --> 01:14:14,830
神速力之核的力量让他不能集中精神
The nexus power had him so distracted,

1325
01:14:14,830 --> 01:14:17,230
他完全忽视了自己周围的一切
he was totally unaware of his surroundings.

1326
01:14:17,230 --> 01:14:19,260
我绝对不能让那样的事发生在我身上
No way would I ever let that happen to me.

1327
01:14:19,270 --> 01:14:22,770
归还神速之核的力量一直就是我计划的……一部分
Returning the nexus was always a part of my... plan,

1328
01:14:22,770 --> 01:14:26,840
而且这些也是你们大家一直想要教导我的事
and these were all the things you guys were trying to teach me.

1329
01:14:27,440 --> 01:14:29,270
谢谢大家
Thank you.

1330
01:14:29,270 --> 01:14:31,970
要不是有你们这样的朋友，我将会永远失去我的超能力
Without friends like you, I would have lost my powers forever.

1331
01:14:31,980 --> 01:14:34,380
而我们也得被迫永久退休了
And we would have been retired forever.

1332
01:14:34,380 --> 01:14:35,580
这倒提醒我了
That reminds me,

1333
01:14:35,580 --> 01:14:37,650
我们正义联盟有没有什么养老金计划或者……
is there a Justice League pension plan or...

1334
01:14:37,650 --> 01:14:39,850
你回来真是太好了 闪电侠
It's good to have you back, Flash.

1335
01:14:39,850 --> 01:14:42,150
还有了你新得到的智慧的引导
And with newfound wisdom to guide you.

1336
01:14:42,150 --> 01:14:44,450
也许是这样 神奇女侠
That may be true,Wonder Woman,

1337
01:14:44,460 --> 01:14:45,920
但闪电侠才刚刚证明了
but Flash has only proven

1338
01:14:45,930 --> 01:14:48,090
他已经为下一阶段的特训做好准备了
he's ready for the next level of training.

1339
01:14:48,090 --> 01:14:49,890
现在开始真正的考验的是
Now begins the true test

1340
01:14:49,890 --> 01:14:52,860
闪电侠精神上的敏锐和不屈不挠
of Flash's mental acuity and fortitude.

1341
01:14:52,860 --> 01:14:54,960
我准备的考验异常残酷
The training crucible I have prepared

1342
01:14:54,970 --> 01:14:56,770
将摧毁他隐藏在内心的软弱
will destroy hidden weakness

1343
01:14:56,770 --> 01:14:59,570
锻炼出内心所需要的强大的力量来……
and forge the inner strength required to...

1344
01:14:59,570 --> 01:15:01,170
唔 听起来很棒 蝙蝠侠
Hmm. It sounds great, Batman.

1345
01:15:01,170 --> 01:15:02,870
我们开始吧
Let's get started on that.

1346
01:15:02,880 --> 01:15:05,370
吃完小点心再开始
Right after a little snack.

1347
01:15:05,380 --> 01:15:08,910
神速力之核已经被送回了神速力之地
The nexus has been returned to the Speed Force.

1348
01:15:08,910 --> 01:15:12,450
宇宙已经重获秩序
And order has been restored to the universe.

1349
01:15:12,450 --> 01:15:14,150
所有这些只用了……
And all it took was...

1350
01:15:14,150 --> 01:15:17,150
魔力呀 宝贝 只是一点小小的魔力
♪ Magic, baby It's just a little magic ♪

1351
01:15:17,150 --> 01:15:19,490
- 扎塔娜 - 起不对……
- Zatanna.- Yrros.


